snippet.title: Destiny 2: Shadowkeep - Official Trailer | Stadia Connect
snippet.description:
You haven’t seen darkness. Not yet.

A great battle approaches. What was once a symbol of humanity’s determination has now become a battleground against the Nightmares of our past.

Destiny 2: Shadowkeep launches on Stadia as part of Destiny 2: The Collection later this fall.

Watch the full Stadia Connect: g.co/stadiaconnect
